<html>
  <head>
    <title>Cubing Contests</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; word-wrap: break-word; } .unofficial-events-contents { margin:
      1.5rem 0.5rem; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 10px; background-color: #eee; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>A new video-based {{eventName}} result has been submitted and is pending approval by the admin team.</p>

    <p>Created by: {{creatorUsername}}</p>
    <p>Format: {{roundFormat}}</p>
    <p>Best: {{best}}</p>
    {{#if average}}
      <p>Average: {{average}}</p>
    {{/if}}
    <p>Video link: <a href="{{videoLink}}" target="_blank">{{videoLink}}</a></p>
    {{#if discussionLink}}
      <p>Discussion link: <a href="{{discussionLink}}" target="_blank">{{discussionLink}}</a></p>
    {{/if}}

    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to send a reply to this email. <strong>Make sure to use "Reply All"!</strong></p>
    
    <p>@CC Admin: Review the result and approve it so it becomes publicly visible on the website.</p>
  </body>
</html>